#: ../../changelog.md:5
msgid "**Improved support for MeSO-net**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:7
msgid "MeSO-net has two network codes for different time periods:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:9
msgid "`0131` for data after 20170401"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:10
msgid "`0231` for data 20080516-20170401"
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.md:12
msgid ""
"In previous versions, you need to know the above information and choose the "
"correct network code when requesting data before or after 20170401. In this "
"new version, HinetPy can automatically switch the network code for you, "
"depending on the data time you're requesting. Note that you will get an "
"error if the time span you requested crosses the date 20170401."
msgstr ""

